        <item>
            <title>【教学】iOS 18.2 Image Playground 好玩教学，生成自己样子 Emoji + 用自己样制作卡通图片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/imageplayground/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=imageplayground</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/imageplayground/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 12:32:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Intelligence]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS 18.2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Image Playground]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18.2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18.2 beta]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277364</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前我们报道过，Apple iOS 18.2 beta 正式加入了 Image Playground 新功能（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/24/image-playground-in-ios-18-2/software/ios-app/">相关报道</a>），现在使用 Image Playground 生成图片时，可以使用多种方式生成心仪图片，例如使用文字 Prompt、选择 Apple 推荐的关键字、在相簿选择图片等。现在让小编和大家分享如何使用这个 Apple 官方图像生成功能吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0438-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0438-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0438.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0438-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编利用沙律照片生成的图像，像真人吗？</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278304" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/photo_62197477204034-1-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/photo_62197477204034-1-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/photo_62197477204034-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Genmoji 可以生成带有自己样子的 Emoji，可以更准确表达感情</p><h2>需求</h2><p>已升级至 iOS 18.2 Beta 的 iPhone 15 Pro 系列或 iPhone 16，升级后系统会自动在主画面新增「Playground」应用程式，让用家以文字生成卡通图片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241127201001-541x580.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241127201001-541x580.jpg 541w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241127201001.jpg 839w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 541px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编使用的是 iPhone 16， 升级至 iOS 18.2 Developer Beta 后，主画面会出现「Playground」应用程式</p><h2>设定</h2><p>要注意的是，你需要将电话语言、Siri &amp; Apple Intelligence 的语言设定为 English<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>（US）</strong></span>，地区亦需要设定为 United States。目前 Image Playground 仍然属测试阶段，需要申请轮候一段时间方可使用。</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277389" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apple_imageplaygroun-543x580.jpg" alt="" width="543" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apple_imageplaygroun-543x580.jpg 543w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apple_imageplaygroun.jpg 840w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 543px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲Siri 语言需要是 English（US），另外 iPhone 的语言亦须设定为 English（US），地区亦须设定为 United States</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277394" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241126184406-541x580.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241126184406-541x580.jpg 541w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241126184406.jpg 839w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 541px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点选 Request Early Access，然后点 Done</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277383 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0440-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0440-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0440.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编轮候了约 2 星期方能够试玩</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
