        <item>
            <title>Jaguar Type 00 概念车登场，大胆新设计展现全电动化愿景</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/jaguar-type-00/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jaguar-type-00</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/jaguar-type-00/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 12:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[jaguar]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278922</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Jaguar 先前公布全新品牌形象，前衞设计引起网上不少讨论，而最近采用这设计元素的概念车终于现身，与一直以来的风格截然不同。<br /><span id="more-1278922"></span></p><p>Jaguar 在迈阿密艺术周发表的全新概念车 Type 00，可说是他们以全新形象向全电动化转型的预览。据 Jaguar 表示，概念车体现了他们「生动而极具张力的现代主义」设计哲学，重新诠释品牌创办人「Copy Nothing」的理念。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Type 00 采用为未来电动车系列而设的 Jaguar Electric Architecture 电动架构，外型融合修长引擎盖、流线型车顶和船尾设计，配备 23 吋合金铃。车厢采用蝴蝶门设计，搭配手工黄铜饰边和悬浮式仪表板，设计前衞独特。配色方面则有向迈阿密 Art Deco 风格致敬的「Miami Pink」，以及体现英国传承的「London Blue」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278928" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende-694x300.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende-694x300.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04-694x300.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04-694x300.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Jaguar 计划在 2025 年底推出首款新世代量产电动车，预计为一款四门 GT 跑车，目标实现 WLTP 续航力 770 公里，快充 15 分钟可增加 321 公里续航距离。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr-690x580.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr-690x580.jpg 690w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr.jpg 1071w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 690px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Jaguar 首席外观设计师 Constantino Segui Gilabert 表示：「Jaguar 绝不容许平庸。当您首次看到全新 Jaguar 时，它必须让人感到惊叹，像是从未见过的存在。Type 00 引人注目，就像过去所有出类拔萃的 Jaguar 一样，并拥有强大的存在感，彰显出独特的英国创意与原创精神，赞扬艺术，体现了非凡现代主义的精髓。」</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/jaguar-type-00/life-tech/auto/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>1.2 亿太空垃圾需管制，全球数据共享成解救关键</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/space-garbage/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=space-garbage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/space-garbage/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278867</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现时由政府或私人企业将衞星发上太空的数量愈来愈多，长远或会影响香港的通讯系统。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1278869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/1140x641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/1140x641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/1140x641.jpg 1140w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">废弃衞星和太空垃圾日益增多，威胁瘫痪近地轨道，危及全球通讯和导航系统。美国太空追踪公司 Slingshot Aerospace 数据显示，LEO 现有逾 14,000 颗衞星，约 3,500 颗已停止运作，加上估计 1.2 亿件太空碎片，仅数千件体积足够大到可被追踪。此严峻情况促使联合国太空交通协调委员会于 10 月下旬紧急呼吁采取行动。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">委员会促请建立共享轨道物体数据库及国际框架，以追踪和管理太空垃圾。委员会联合主席 Aarti Holla-Maini 强调，公私营运商之间必须共享信息，以避免碰撞，保障近地轨道的安全。GPS、衞星电视和天气预报等服务一旦受阻，后果不堪设想。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">现时缺乏所有航天国家都能使用的中央系统，构成重大挑战。部分国家愿意共享数据，但基于安全顾虑，特别是衞星的军事双重用途，进展缓慢。国际合作刻不容缓，以避免近地轨道及相关重要服务瘫痪。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">来源：</span><a href="https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202412020138.aspx"><span style="font-weight: 400;">中央社</span></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/space-garbage/fun-tech/">1.2 亿太空垃圾需管制，全球数据共享成解救关键</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/space-garbage/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
