            <title>Sony PlayStation 30 周年更新玩复古，PS5 可使用元祖 PS 至 PS4 开机画面</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/sony-brings-back-original-playstation-boot-screen-with-ps5-anniversary-update/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-brings-back-original-playstation-boot-screen-with-ps5-anniversary-update</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/sony-brings-back-original-playstation-boot-screen-with-ps5-anniversary-update/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:30:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[playstation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PlayStation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PS5]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278948</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>PlayStation（PS）今年迎来 30 周年，Sony 方面庆祝活动多多，除了推出 30 周年限定版 PS5 Pro 、开设 PlayStation 网站（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/ps2-160m-sales/game-channel/">相关报道</a>）外，近日推出了限时 PS5 更新，「回带」让无数玩家怀念的「Sony Computer Entertainment」开机画面。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278958" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot_2024_12_0-1-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot_2024_12_0-1-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot_2024_12_0-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：PlayStation@YouTube</p><p>Sony 稍早时分推出限时更新，现在玩家可以自订 PS5 主题介面，使用 PS1 至 PS4 四代主机主题介面，另外 Sony 亦推出了一款 30 周年纪念主题。每次开机时，PS5 都会按照你选择的主机主题，播放相应的启动画面，例如选择了 PS 的话，就会播放经典 Sony Computer Entertainment 标志，另外更有 PS 开机音效 。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F2960323684117924%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=560&amp;t=0" width="560" height="314" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>Sony PlayStation 另外亦制作了一条影片，感谢玩家 30 年来的支持。无论你小时候玩哪一代 PlayStation，相信看到今次 PS5 限时更新，以及下面 Sony PlayStation 制作的影片后，也会觉得感动吧。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278959" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：PlayStation@YouTube</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1278955" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/30thanniversary_than-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：PlayStation@YouTube</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_12566"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KkmonzpHVRg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2024/12/PlayStation-5-Pro-New-loading-Screen.jpg">Gizmodo</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311112/playstation-30th-anniversary-psx-boot-sequence-ps5-update">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KkmonzpHVRg&amp;ab_channel=PlayStation">PlayStation@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
